---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { SUPPORT_EMAIL } from "../../config/site";
---

<BaseLayout
    title="Terms of Service - Kafadar"
    description="Terms of Service for Kafadar."
>
    <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Terms of Service</h1>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-10">Last updated: February 17, 2026</p>

        <article class="space-y-8 text-gray-700 leading-7">
            <section class="space-y-3">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">1. Acceptance</h2>
                <p>
                    By downloading or using Kafadar, you agree to these Terms of Service.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="space-y-3">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
                    2. Eligibility and Account
                </h2>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                    <li>The service is intended for users aged 13 and older.</li>
                    <li>
                        You are responsible for account security and for activities under
                        your account.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="space-y-3">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
                    3. User Content
                </h2>
                <p>
                    You are responsible for content you create or share. Illegal, harmful,
                    abusive, or rights-infringing content is prohibited.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="space-y-3">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
                    4. Prohibited Conduct
                </h2>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                    <li>Unauthorized access attempts or security violations.</li>
                    <li>Spam, malware, fraud, impersonation, or abuse.</li>
                    <li>Unlawful disclosure of other people's personal information.</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="space-y-3">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
                    5. Intellectual Property
                </h2>
                <p>
                    The software, branding, design, and non-user content of Kafadar are
                    owned by Kafadar and protected by applicable laws.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="space-y-3">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
                    6. Third-Party Services
                </h2>
                <p>
                    The app may rely on third-party services (app stores, infrastructure,
                    ads). Those services are governed by their own terms.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="space-y-3">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
                    7. Changes and Termination
                </h2>
                <p>
                    We may modify, suspend, or terminate the service. Accounts that violate
                    these terms may be restricted or terminated.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="space-y-3">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
                    8. Disclaimer and Liability
                </h2>
                <p>
                    The service is provided "as is." To the extent allowed by law, we are
                    not liable for indirect, incidental, or consequential damages.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="space-y-3">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">9. Updates</h2>
                <p>
                    We may update these terms. Material changes will be reflected with a
                    new date on this page.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="space-y-3">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">10. Contact</h2>
                <p>
                    Questions:
                    <a
                        class="text-primary-600 hover:underline"
                        href={`mailto:${SUPPORT_EMAIL}`}>{SUPPORT_EMAIL}</a
                    >
                </p>
            </section>
        </article>
    </main>
</BaseLayout>
